data.description: This unit is a 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhome offers the ultimate comfort for you and your family. Once inside, you are greeted by a warm and inviting family room, creating a cozy atmosphere for gatherings and relaxation. The open layout seamlessly connects the family room to the eat-in kitchen. The kitchen comes complete with a convenient pantry, providing ample storage for all your culinary needs. On the main floor, you'll also find a half bathroom, ensuring privacy and convenience for you and your guests. Upstairs you will find two spacious sized bedrooms, each with its own full bathroom. Outside, you can relax on the charming private patio, perfect for enjoying morning coffee or gatherings with family and friends.  Conveniently located in Hiram, this property boasts a fantastic location with easy access to schools, parks, shopping, and more! Contact us today to schedule your showing.
